---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Forge RPA"
  description="Enterprise finance and operations automation powered by a proprietary framework. Combining 30 years of financial operations expertise with self-improving automation systems."
  heroTitle="Enterprise Finance and Operations Automation Framework"
  heroSubtitle="Built by someone with 30 years in financial operations and controllership. Our proprietary framework combines deep domain expertise with self-improving automation capabilities. Our deepest craft is finance-grade automation—and we apply the same rigor to operations and administrative flows when they are rules-based and systems-accessible."
>
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Background -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Forge RPA was founded on a simple observation: the people who understand business processes best are rarely the ones building the automations. That gap leads to solutions that look good in demos but fall apart in production.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          With 30 years of hands-on experience in financial operations and controllership, we have closed the books, managed reconciliations, prepared financial reports, and lived the daily challenges that finance teams face—alongside the operational handoffs and data feeds that land in finance. This practical experience shapes every automation we build.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Our proprietary enterprise framework combines this domain expertise with self-improving automation capabilities, persistent learning systems, and deep Microsoft 365 integration. Proven in finance but applicable to other operational processes. The result is practical, maintainable automation with built-in governance that delivers real ROI — not just impressive demos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Experience</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-light rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">📊</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Finance & Operations</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              30 years of hands-on experience in financial operations, controllership, and systems transformation across manufacturing, utilities, healthcare, and financial services. We understand the real challenges finance teams face because we've lived them.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-light rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🤖</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Automation Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Creator of a proprietary enterprise automation framework featuring persistent learning systems, self-improving capabilities, and deep Microsoft 365 integration. Focused on building automation that is both powerful and maintainable for finance teams.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Philosophy -->
      <div class="mb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-charcoal-light rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic">
          "The best finance automations aren't built by pure technologists or pure accountants — they're built by people who have actually managed financial operations and understand both the business process and how to automate it effectively at enterprise scale."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Industries -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Industries Served</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Manufacturing', 'Utilities', 'Healthcare', 'Insurance', 'Financial Services', 'Professional Services'].map((industry) => (
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark font-medium rounded-lg text-sm">
              {industry}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm">Our proprietary framework has been successfully applied across multiple industries. The core approach — combining deep finance domain expertise with self-improving automation capabilities — applies to any organization with complex manual finance and accounting processes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    heading="Let's Talk About Your Finance Processes"
    subtext="30 minutes. No sales pitch. We'll discuss your specific challenges in month-end close, accounts payable, reconciliations, or reporting, and explore how our framework could deliver results for your team."
    ctaText="Book a Discovery Call"
    ctaLink="/book"
  />
</PageLayout>
